	<LINE>Postmasters in the United Kingdom have power</LINE>
	<LINE>to transfer to other offices in the United Kingdom</LINE>
	<LINE>payment of colonial and foreign orders originally</LINE>
	<LINE>drawn on their own offices.</LINE>
	<LINE>Orders issued in the United Kingdom on Belgium,</LINE>
