	<LINE>Indian Possessions, India, Norway, Egypt, and the</LINE>
	<LINE>British Colonies, are payable for twelve months</LINE>
	<LINE>after the ^month of issue. Orders issued in the</LINE>
	<LINE>United Kingdom on the German Empire and the</LINE>
	<LINE>United States of America are subject to the regula-</LINE>
	<LINE>tions which govern the payment of Money Orders</LINE>
	<LINE>in those countries. Orders issued in France on the</LINE>
